By Chibuike Nwabuko Abuja (Sundiata Post) – Senator representing Kebbi Central senatorial district, Senator Adamu Aliero has been named as the Chairman of adhoc committee on legislative agenda. He was unveiled as chairman of the committee on Tuesday by the Senate President, Senator Ahmed Lawan at the floor of the red chamber during plenary. Senator Adamu Aliero and his team are to come up with the legislative agenda for the 9th Senate. The committee was given fourteen (14) days to complete the assignment. Details Later….